---
title: Introduction
description: Discover the PolyAI partner ecosystem
---

Our integrations give you the power to plug PolyAI's voice and chat assistants into your existing and new projects on a range of leading platforms.
From managing reservations with [OpenTable](/integrations/opentable) to using [Salesforce](/integrations/salesforce) for live agent handoff, each integration is designed to streamline your
workflows and deliver outstanding customer experiences.

Click on one of the tiles below for information on capabilities and integration instructions:
